flowchart TD
    Start([package linked app]) --> ParseArgs[Parse app name]
    ParseArgs --> BuildPath[Build app path in ~/projects/]
    
    BuildPath --> CheckApp{App dir exists?}
    CheckApp -->|No| AppNotFound[Error: App not found]
    AppNotFound --> FailExit([Failure])
    
    CheckApp -->|Yes| RunLinked[Run composer linked]
    RunLinked --> ParseOutput[Parse output lines]
    ParseOutput --> ExtractPackages[Extract package names and paths]
    
    ExtractPackages --> CheckEmpty{Any packages?}
    CheckEmpty -->|No| ReportNone[No linked packages]
    CheckEmpty -->|Yes| ReportList[List packages with paths]
    
    ReportNone --> SuccessExit([Success])
    ReportList --> SuccessExit
